  <title>Add Mechanism-Editor</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword>Add<keyword>Mechanism-Editor (Mechanism)</keyword></keyword>
    <keyword>Menu<keyword>Add &gt; Add Mechanism</keyword></keyword>
    <keyword>Model toolbar<keyword>Add Mechanism</keyword></keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Add Mechanism-Editor</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_">What is a Mechanism?</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">A <text styleclass="Element-Header">Mechanism</text> element defines the workspace of one <text styleclass="VariableName">Mechanism-Editor</text> &#160;- Mechanism name-tab, graphic-area, XY-axes, and <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-BasePart">Base-Part</link>.</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">To add a </text><text styleclass="Element-Header">Mechanism</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"> element, you must select a </text><text styleclass="Element-Header">Plane</text>. </para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">The XY-axes of the <text styleclass="VariableName">Mechanism-Editor</text>&apos;s workspace and of the <text styleclass="Element-Header">Plane</text> you select are coincident and coplanar.</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">There is no limit to the number of </text><text styleclass="Element-Header">Mechanism</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"> elements you can add to your model. </text>You add all other element-types to <text styleclass="VariableName">Mechanism-Editors</text>. </para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_">Add Mechanism</para>
    <list id="0" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#83;&#84;&#69;&#80;&#32;&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#58;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo STEP" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="HowTo STEP"><text style="font-style:normal;">Start the Add Mechanism command:</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="2" style="cell-padding:1px; border-width:0px; border-spacing:0px; border-collapse:collapse; cell-border-width:1px; border-color:#343400; border-style:solid;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:middle">
        <td style="width:240px;">
          <para styleclass="Image Caption"><image src="MD-Toolbar-Model-AddMechanism-A.ipp" scale="-99.90%" figurelistinclude="0"><caption><![CDATA[Model elements toolbar]]></caption><imagemap><area shape="rect" coords="1,50,237,90" type="topiclink" href="MD-Modelelements(Model)-AddMechanism"><title>ModelAddMech</title></area></imagemap></image></para>
        </td>
        <td style="vertical-align:middle;">
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="2">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td style="vertical-align:bottom; width:41px;">
                <para styleclass="VariableName" style="text-align:right;"><image src="MD-Icon-AddMechanismEditor.ipp" scale="100.00%" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
              </td>
              <td>
                <list id="1" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Body Table" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Text">Click </text><text styleclass="T_Menu">Add menu &gt; Add Mechanism</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
                </list>
                <para styleclass="VariableName">OR</para>
                <list id="2" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="B Bullets" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="B Bullets"><text styleclass="Body Text">Click</text><text styleclass="Interface">&#32;</text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Modelelements(Model)" styleclass="T_Menu">Model elements toolbar</link><text styleclass="T_Menu"> &gt; Add Mechanism</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
                </list>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">The <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Command-Manager" styleclass="Interface">Command-Manager</link> starts. It has one selection-box.</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <list id="3" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#83;&#84;&#69;&#80;&#32;&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#58;&#32;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="false" legalstyle="false" startfrom="2" styleclass="HowTo STEP" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="HowTo STEP">Select a Plane </li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="2">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:240px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:right;"><image src="MD-CM-AddMechanismEditor.png" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"><caption><![CDATA[Command-Manager]]></caption></image></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:right;"><image src="MD-CM-AddMechanismEditor-Plane.png" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"><caption><![CDATA[Command-Manager - Plane element]]></caption></image></para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Normal">The </text><text styleclass="Interface">Command-Manager</text><text styleclass="Normal"> has one selection-box. </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Normal">You must select a </text><text styleclass="Element">Plane</text><text styleclass="Normal">.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">If you cannot see a <text styleclass="Element">Plane</text>: <text styleclass="Body Text HowTo">Enable </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Visibility-SolidsInMechanisms" styleclass="T_Menu">Show Solids in Mechanisms</link><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo">. </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td style="border-top:none; border-right:none; border-bottom:none;">
                <list id="4" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Body Table" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="Body Table">Click a <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Plane" styleclass="Element">Plane</link> in <text styleclass="Body Text">the graphic-area</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
                </list>
                <para styleclass="Interface2">or<text styleclass="Body Text">&#32;</text></para>
                <list id="5" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Body Table" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Text">Click a </text><text styleclass="Element">Plane</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> in the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Assembly-Tree" styleclass="Interface">Assembly-Tree</link><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
                </list>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text">The </text><text styleclass="Element">Plane</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> is now in the selection-box in the </text><text styleclass="Interface">Command-Manager</text><text styleclass="Body Text">.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <list id="6" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#83;&#84;&#69;&#80;&#32;&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#58;&#32;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="false" legalstyle="false" startfrom="3" styleclass="HowTo STEP" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="HowTo STEP">Complete the command</li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="2">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:240px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center;"><image src="MD-CM-OK-AddMechanismEditor-Plane.ipp" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"><title>Command-Manager - Plane element</title><caption><![CDATA[Command-Manager - 'OK']]></caption></image></para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Normal">You must click the &apos;tick&apos; to complete the command.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:middle">
              <td style="border-top:none; border-right:none; border-bottom:none;">
                <list id="7" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Bullets" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="Bullets">Click <image src="OK-tiny-11-15.png" scale="100.00%" figurelistinclude="0"></image> in the <text styleclass="Interface">Command-Manager</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
                </list>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Interface2">Result</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <list id="8" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Bullets" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="Bullets">The <text styleclass="Interface">Command-Manager</text> closes.<text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Bullets">You <text styleclass="VariableName">jump</text> immediately to a new <text styleclass="VariableName">Mechanism-Editor</text> workspace</li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The </text><text styleclass="Element">Mechanism</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> element is new element that is a</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo"> child to the </text><text styleclass="Element">Plane</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo"> you select</text><text styleclass="VariableName">.</text></li>
          </list>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="VariableName"><text styleclass="Interface2">RESULT</text><text styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_">:</text> Workspace</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="2" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="MD-MECHANISM-EDITOR.ipp" scale="-99.90%" figurelistinclude="0"><title>Mechanism Editor - Identify</title><caption><![CDATA[Mechanism-Editor workspace]]></caption></image><text styleclass="Body Text">&#32;</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <para styleclass="Body Text">The workspace of each Mechanism-Editor has many important features</para>
                <para styleclass="Body Table"><image src="Red-14-1b.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption"> : </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-BasePart" styleclass="Element">Base-Part</link><text styleclass="Body Text"> with </text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">a rectangular </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Part-Outline" styleclass="Interface">Part-Outline</link></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Table"><image src="Red-14-2.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"> : </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Mechanism tab</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"> &#160;</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Table"><image src="Red-14-3.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"> : </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Toolbars</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"> (left and right of the graphic-area) </text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Table"><image src="Red-14-4.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"> : </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Graphic-Area</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Table"><image src="Red-14-5.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"> : </text><text styleclass="VariableName" style="color:#ff0000;">Local</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">&#32;</text><text styleclass="VariableName">XY-axes</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"> of the </text><text styleclass="Interface">Mechanism-Editor</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> and </text><text styleclass="Element">Base-Part</text></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_">&#32;<text styleclass="Interface2">Result</text><text styleclass="VariableName">: Assembly-Tree</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="2" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="MD-AT-AddMechanism-New.ipp" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="VariableName">The Mechanism element in the Assembly-Tree:</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <para styleclass="Bullets"><text styleclass="Element">Plane4</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> - you select to add the </text><text styleclass="Element">Mechanism</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> element: &#160;</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text">(New)<text styleclass="Element"> Mechanism2 -</text> a child to <text styleclass="Element">Plane4</text>, and coplanar with the <text styleclass="VariableName">XY axes</text> of <text styleclass="Element">Plane4</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text">(New) <text styleclass="Element">BasePart2</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"> &#160;- a child to </text><text styleclass="Element">Mechanism2</text> and coplanar with the <text styleclass="VariableName">XY axes</text> of <text styleclass="Element">Plane4</text></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Table">The <text styleclass="Interface">XY-Plane</text> of <text styleclass="Element">Plane4, Mechanism2,</text> and <text styleclass="Element">Base-Part2</text> are coplanar.</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
